# Chana Masala

Based on [https://twosleevers.com/pressure-cooker-homestyle-chana-masala/](https://twosleevers.com/pressure-cooker-homestyle-chana-masala) ([wayback](http://web.archive.org/web/20260113120926/https://twosleevers.com/pressure-cooker-homestyle-chana-masala/)) and [https://ministryofcurry.com/instant-pot-chana-masala-recipe/](https://ministryofcurry.com/instant-pot-chana-masala-recipe) ([wayback](http://web.archive.org/web/20251207225254/https://ministryofcurry.com/instant-pot-chana-masala-recipe/))

